The,HP,Public,Cloud,is,an,enterprise,quality,public,cloud,that,offers,a,variety,of,public,services,including,a,Domain,Name,Service,DNS,The,HP,Cloud,DNS,allows,users,to,manage,their,DNS,zones,and,records,in,an,efficient,and,secure,manner,The,service,uses,Anycast,routing,to,improve,its,reliability,speed,and,uptime,HP,Cloud,DNS,comes,with,a,set,of,APIs,that,allow,users,to,display,create,modify,and,delete,DNS,records,programmatically,via,REST,calls